Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.03,0:00:04.72,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The 737 MAX was sold as a
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.72,0:00:06.28,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,familiar airplane.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.28,0:00:07.85,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,That was the commercial
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.85,0:00:09.37,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.37,0:00:10.89,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Airlines could keep crews,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.89,0:00:13.58,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,schedules, and training\Nclose to the old
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.58,0:00:15.42,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,737.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.42,0:00:17.25,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Then Boeing put larger CFM\NLEAP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.25,0:00:19.31,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,engines on the aircraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.25,0:00:22.42,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,They sat farther forward\Nand higher on
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.42,0:00:23.91,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,the wing, and under\Ncertain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.91,0:00:26.15,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,high-angle-of-attack\Nconditions, the jet
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.15,0:00:27.70,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,could pitch up\Ndifferently.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.21,0:00:30.35,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,MCAS was built to make\Nthat new
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.35,0:00:31.72,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,behavior feel familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.72,0:00:33.09,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,But the system
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:35.41,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,could move the stabilizer\Nfrom one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.41,0:00:37.13,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,angle-of-attack sensor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.13,0:00:38.86,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Pilots were not
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.86,0:00:40.84,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,clearly trained that it\Nexisted by name.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.24,0:00:44.61,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,After Lion Air 610, the\Nwarning still
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.61,0:00:47.13,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,was not reclassified fast\Nenough as an
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:48.66,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,architectural problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.66,0:00:50.19,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The plane had
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.19,0:00:51.65,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.65,0:00:53.11,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The story told to the\Npeople
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.11,0:00:54.03,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,flying it had not.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.83,0:00:58.00,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Small causes, massive\Nconsequences.
